    "### Load the top 50 marker gene table from Allen Whole Mouse Brain (isocortex subset)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",

   "source": [
    "Here, we load the top marker genes precomputed using COSG on Allen Institute's Whole Mouse Brain Atlas (isocortex subset), and other marker gene lists are also compatible. Precomputed marker gene sets for multiple studies are available in [PIASOmarkerDB](https://piaso.org/piasomarkerdb)."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "b3687692-2c06-4d2f-94da-f981e670d6b3",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [

   ]

    "Here because we used the marker genes identified from finer clustering of `Subclass`, so we set `extract_cell_type  = True`, `delimiter_cell_type  = '-'`, you can set `extract_cell_type  = False` if the input marker genes resolution already matched to the annotations you are interested:"
   ]

    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "Predicting cell types based on marker gene scores...\n",
      "Smoothing cell type predictions...\n",
      "Smoothing cell type predictions from 'Subclass_predicted_raw' using 9-nearest neighbors\n",
      "Smoothed predictions stored in adata.obs['Subclass_predicted_smoothed']\n",
      "Modified 1141 cell labels (6.55% of total)\n",
      "Cell type prediction completed. Results saved to:\n",
      "  - adata.obs['Subclass_predicted']: predicted cell types\n",
      "  - adata.obsm['Subclass_predicted_score']: full score matrix\n",
      "  - adata.obs['Subclass_predicted_score']: maximum scores\n",
      "  - adata.obs['Subclass_predicted_raw']: original unsmoothed predictions\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "piaso.tl.predictCellTypeByMarker(\n",
    "    adata,\n",
    "    marker_gene_set=cosgMarkerDB[:50], ### Use the top 50 marker genes,\n",
    "    score_method = 'piaso',\n",
    "    score_layer = 'infog',\n",
    "    use_score  = True,\n",
    "    max_workers = 32,\n",
    "    smooth_prediction = True,\n",
    "    use_rep = 'X_pca_harmony', ### Use the specified low-dimensional cell embeddings for kNN graph-based cell type prediction smoothing\n",
    "    k_nearest_neighbors = 9,\n",
    "    return_confidence  = False,\n",
    "    use_existing_adjacency_graph = False,\n",
    "    use_faiss = False,\n",
    "    key_added  = 'Subclass_predicted',\n",
    "    extract_cell_type  = True, delimiter_cell_type  = '-', ## Set True to extract the subclass, as now it's clusters of subclass level\n",
    "    \n",
    "    inplace  = True,\n",
    "    random_seed = 1927,\n",
    "    verbosity = 1,\n",
    "    n_jobs  = -1,\n",
    ")"
   ]
  },
